Document: MarginContainer
Path: godot/classes/class_margincontainer.rst
Summary: Theme properties for offsetting direct children inside a MarginContainer from each edge.

Property: margin_bottom (int): Offsets towards the inside direct children of the container by this amount of pixels from the bottom. Default: 0.
Property: margin_left (int): Offsets towards the inside direct children of the container by this amount of pixels from the left. Default: 0.
Property: margin_right (int): Offsets towards the inside direct children of the container by this amount of pixels from the right. Default: 0.
Property: margin_top (int): Offsets towards the inside direct children of the container by this amount of pixels from the top. Default: 0.